 147:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****       1) by calling CMSIS function SystemCoreClockUpdate()
 148:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****       2) by calling HAL API function HAL_RCC_GetHCLKFreq()
 149:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****       3) each time HAL_RCC_ClockConfig() is called to configure the system clock frequency
 150:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****          Note: If you use this function to configure the system clock; then there
 151:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****                is no need to call the 2 first functions listed above, since SystemCoreClock
 152:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****                variable is updated automatically.
 153:Core/Src/system_stm32g4xx.c ****   */
